('AZP', 'AdZap', 5, 'Test your marketing skills!', '<img src="/2013/images/events/Content-Marketing(2)_resized.jpg" alt="Content-Marketing(2).jpg"/>\r\n\r\n<br>\r\nThis event is an ode to all the smooth talkers out there. <br/>\r\nRack up the creative side of your brain and convince us to buy anything - from a broken needle to a flattened tyre.||sec||Rules and Regulation||ttl||\r\n<li>2 teams per college</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Maximum number of 3 participants per team</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Written prelims will be held</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Adzap and potpourri will be two subsequent rounds</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Dialogue and narration can be in English/Malayalam as per choice</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Weightage will be give to spontaneity, humour and creativity</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Points:  (20, 15, 10)</li>||sec||Prize Money||ttl||First -  INR 3500<br>\r\nSecond - INR 2000<br>\r\nThird -  INR 1000<br>', 'AdZap, potpourri, marketing, wacky, creative, sales, challenge, team ', 'Stebin Varghese||@||9995591911||@||adzap||0||Shreya Bhatia||@||9633102336||@||adzap||0||||@||||@||adzap||0||', 'First -  INR 3500<br>\r\nSecond - INR 2000<br>\r\nThir', '1||@||3', 0),
('BBL', 'Basketball', 14, 'Higher education... you know, 6â€™8â€³, 6â€™9â€³, 6â€™10â€', 'The game that explodes with excitement.<br/> \r\nWhere it is never too late for things to change,<br/>  \r\nWhere character is not built but revealed.<br/>  \r\nThe fervour of victory will send shivers this Ragam.<br/>  \r\nThere will be raw excitement flavoured with genius, skill and strength.<br/><br/>   \r\nSo if you breathe this game, if this is all you live for, the hoop is open, the net is hot, come make that shot.<br/> \r\n||sec||Rules and Regulations||ttl||<ul>\r\n<li>FIBA rules applicable.</li>\r\n<li>Teams should report to the basket ball court half an hour before their match.</li>\r\n<li>All the players of the team should have the same colour of jersey with printed numbers.</li>\r\n<li>Use of abusive or foul language during the play can lead to technical fouls or expulsion.</li>\r\n<li>Jewellery of any kind is not allowed and nails have to be cut.</li>\r\n<li>Decisions of the referee and the organizing committee will be final and binding.</li>\r\n<li>Min Number of players in menâ€™s/womenâ€™s team: 5</li>\r\n<li>Max Number of players in men&#39;s/womenâ€™s team: 12</li>\r\n<li>These rules are merely guidelines and the organizing body reserves the right to make changes without prior information.</li>\r\n<li>Participating teams should send in the following details to basketball@ragam.org.in on or before March 10th:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>College Name (and Team Name, if any)</li>\r\n<li>Category (Men&#39;s/Women&#39;s)</li>\r\n<li>Name and Contact Info of the Team Leader</li>\r\n<li>List of Team members</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li>Participating teams will be screened on first-come-first-serve basis.</li>\r\n<li>Registration will be confirmed only after receiving the confirmation letter.</li>\r\n<li>Registration fee :  INR 1200/- per team</li>\r\n<li>Hospitality/Accommodation fees: INR 50/- (a caution deposit of INR 50/- will also be collected, which will be refunded at the return of utilities provided)</li>\r\n</ul>||sec||Prize Money||ttl||First - INR 6000<br/>\r\nSecond - INR 4000<br/>\r\n(in both menâ€™s and womenâ€™s categories)<br/>\r\n', 'basket, ball, basketball,nba, ', 'Amith A C (Menâ€™s Coordinator)||@||7736464873||@||basketball||0||Panchami Menon (Womenâ€™s Coordinator)||@||7736199036||@||basketball||0||||@||||@||basketball||0||', 'First - INR 6000<br/>\r\nSecond - INR 4000<br/>\r\n(in', '5||@||12', 0),
('BRL', 'Breakup Letter Writing', 12, 'Breakup as eloquently as you can!', '<img src="/2013/images/events/break-up-65194029168_xlarge_resized.png" alt="break-up-65194029168_xlarge.png"/><br>\r\n<i>Goodbye, the hardest word to say,<br/>\r\n\r\nBut with words from the heart, you should convey,<br/>\r\n\r\nNeither to hurt nor to slay,<br/>\r\n\r\nThe love that died, the friendship forever to stay...</i>||sec||Rules and Regulation||ttl||<ul>\r\n<li> Open event</li>\r\n<li> One entry per person</li>\r\n<li> Any of the two languages (English/Malayalam) may be used  </li>\r\n<li> Entries to be mailed by 21st February , 11:59 pm to breakupletter@ragam.org.in</li>\r\n<li>The winner will be announced online.</li>\r\n</ul>||sec||Prize Money||ttl||First - INR 1000<br/>', '', 'Jain J Abraham||@||9447 928 504||@||breakupletter||0||George Punnen||@||9447 511 575||@||breakupletter||0||Nirmal Sabu||@||9895420189||@||breakupletter||0||', 'First - INR 1000<br/>', '1||@||1', 0),
('CDA', 'Classical Dance', 7, 'Let your grace enchant the audience!', '<img src="/2013/images/events/images (1)(1)_resized.jpg" alt="images (1)(1).jpg"/>\r\n<br><i>Numb the spectators with your grace<br/>\r\nYour movements every eye should trace<br/>\r\nUnveil your story with the progressing beats<br/>\r\nAnd keep us at the edge of our seats!<br/><br/>\r\n</i>\r\n     To express the deepest of emotions with a sway of your body, through a language so ancient that it is divine, is your challenge. Compete at the mother of all stages, â€œRAGAM â€˜13â€ and prove your worth!||sec||Rules and Regulations||ttl||<ul>\r\n<li>Maximum of two participants per college.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Time limit: 10 minutes per participant</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>All forms of Indian classical dance are permitted</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Sound track should be in MP3 format and must be submitted at the registration desk one hour prior to the event</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The usage of breakable items, fire, water, inflammable items or items which may leave the dance floor untidy is strictly prohibited.    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Points: (15, 10, 6)</li>\r\n</ul>||sec||Prize Money||ttl||First  - INR 2500<br>   \r\nSecond - INR 1500<br>  \r\nThird  - INR 1000', 'dance, classical, music, beat, movement, groove', 'Prateeksha||@|| 8129008232||@||classicaldance||0||Pratyusha K ||@||8089833707||@||classicaldance||0||||@||||@||classicaldance||0||', 'First  - INR 2500<br>   \r\nSecond - INR 1500<br>  \r', '1||@||2', 0),
('CHN', 'Choreo Nite', 7, 'The ultimate dance showdown.', '<img src="/2013/images/events/HipHop1_resized.jpg" alt="HipHop1.jpg"/><br>\r\n<i>â€œPop, Lock and Break.<br>\r\nThese were the ingredients chosen<br>\r\nTo create the perfect little dance<br>\r\nBut Professor Utonium added an extra<br> \r\ningredient to the concoction &#8211;<br>\r\nPassion X. <br>\r\nThus, the Hip &#8211; Hop was born.<br>\r\nUsing their ultra cool routines<br>\r\nTeams and battle crews<br>\r\nHave dedicated their lives to entertaining the crowds<br>\r\nAnd the judges at Ragam.â€<br><br/>\r\n</i>\r\nThere are 2 categories:\r\n<li>Themed\r\n<li>Non-Themed\r\n||sec||Rules and Regulations||ttl||<ul>\r\n<li>Maximum of two teams per college\r\n<li>Minimum of 5 members in a team\r\n<li>Time limit : 10 minutes empty to empty\r\n<li>Sound track must be submitted in MP3 format\r\n<li>Breakable items, fire,water, inflammable items or items which may make the dance floor untidy must not be used\r\n<li>Participating teams should upload a video of any of their performance on YouTube and send its URL to groupdance@ragam.org.in on or before March 7th, along with the following details:<br/>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>College Name (and Team Name, if any)</li>\r\n<li>Name and Contact Info of the Team Leader</li>\r\n<li>List of Team members</li>\r\n</ul></li> \r\n<li>Finalists will be screened based on the video sent.</li>\r\n<li>Registration will be confirmed only after receiving the confirmation letter</li>\r\n<li>At least one member of the team should report to the venue before 7:00 pm with their music CDs</li>\r\n<li>Points: (50, 30, 20)</li>\r\n</ul>||sec||Prize Money||ttl||Non-Themed<br>\r\nFirst - INR 30000<br>\r\nSecond - INR 20000<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThemed<br>\r\nFirst - INR 30000<br>\r\nSecond - INR 20000<br>', 'choreo, night, theme, dance', 'Yadu A Menon||@||9746398389||@||groupdance||0||Vijeesh V N||@||9746594938||@||groupdance||0||||@||||@||groupdance||0||', '', '5||@||-', 0),
('CLG', 'Collage', 10, 'Assemble a masterpiece out of bits and pieces.', '<img src="/2013/images/events/557925_508315915876905_898822532_n_resized.jpg" alt="557925_508315915876905_898822532_n.jpg"/>\r\n<br/><q>\r\nI have become intrigued with the combining of seemingly unrelated ideas or images, or the drawing upon the many, sometimes dissimilar, meanings a word might have.</q> <br/>\r\n\r\n-John Barton <br/>\r\n<br>\r\n<br/>\r\nWreck mayhem with scissors, magazines and paper and create a work of art and beauty in ordered randomness.<br/>\r\n\r\n||sec||Rules And Regulations||ttl||\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Open event</li>\r\n<li>Maximum 4 members per team</li>\r\n<li>There will be &#39;On the spot&#39; registration at the venue</li>\r\n<li>Pictures per se cannot be used</li>\r\n<li>Only chart paper will be provided</li>\r\n<li>Topic to be given at the start of the event</li>\r\n<li>Time limit: 90 minutes</li>\r\n<li>Points: (15, 10, 5)</li>\r\n</ul>||sec||Prize Money||ttl||First - INR 1500<br>\r\nSecond - INR 1000<br>\r\nThird - INR 750\r\n', 'collage, magazine, cutting, scissors, paper, art, cut', 'George Punnen ||@||9447511575||@||collage||0||Pratyusha K ||@||8089833707||@||collage||0||||@||||@||collage||0||', 'First - INR 1500<br>\r\nSecond - INR 1000<br>\r\nThird', '2||@||4', 0),
('CLM', 'Classical Music Solo', 9, 'A classic musical extravaganza.', '<img src="/2013/images/events/download (1)_resized.jpg" alt="download (1).jpg"/><br/>\r\n<br>\r\n<i>It is said that Indian classical music is so rich that every human emotion, every restrained feeling in man and nature can be musically expressed and experienced. Enthrall the audience and transform our stage into a magical court of yore with your mesmerizing music.</i>||sec||Rules and Regulations||ttl||<ul>\r\n<li>Two participants per college.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Time limit: 15 minutes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Participants are requested to sing a kirthana preferably of khana ragas (eg.bhairavi, thodi, kamboji etc.) instead of tukadas or light ragas (eg.ranjini, sindhubhairavi etc).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Participants cannot sing more than one kirthana and singing of varnam,jathiswaram, swarajathi (except few cases like Kamakshi) shall not be entertained.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Due credit will be given for singing of raga, neraval and swara for the kirthana.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Decision of judges will be final.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Participants are not supposed to bring accompaniments along with them other than shruthi box.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>No accompaniments(including shruthi box) will be provided.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Points: (10, 6, 4)</li>\r\n</ul>||sec||Prize Money||ttl||First - INR 1000<br>\r\nSecond - INR 600<br>\r\nThird - INR 400<br>', 'Classical, music, carnatic, hindustani, solo, singing ', 'Meerakrishna R ||@||9744797092||@||classicalmusic||0||Ashams K Thomas ||@||9400420584||@||classicalmusic||0||||@||||@||classicalmusic||0||', 'First - INR 1000<br>\r\nSecond - INR 600<br>\r\nThird ', '1||@||1', 0),
('CRD', 'Quiz', 5, '2 College quizzes, 2 Open quizzes', '<img src="/2013/images/events/dice-question-mark-008_resized.jpg" alt="dice-question-mark-008.jpg"/><br/>\r\nNIT Calicut has always produced great quizzers as well as great quiz masters for generations. At this Ragam come and battle it out  with top minds of the country in 2 college quizzes and 2 open quizzes at <b>Crossroads</b>.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n||sec||Open Quizzes||ttl||<u>Mostly Harmless</u> - General Quiz<br/><br/>\r\nâ€œAn infinite question is often destroyed by finite answers. To define everything is to annihilate much that gives us laughter and joy.â€<br/> \r\nThis March the platform is set for you to delve into a maze of grilling rounds with breath taking races to beat the buzzer. For those of you with an encyclopedic repository of knowledge, well, the limelight awaits...<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<u>Lifes A Mela</u> - Music, Entertainment, Literature and Arts Quiz<br/><br/>\r\nThe practise of incorporating trivia from four areas as humongous as these invite perplexed looks from many. But for us at NITC, this has been a time-honored tradition ever since the inception of the quizzing fest. Arguably the best platform to show off all that music, lit and arts news that you have following so closely.||sec||College Quizzes||ttl||<u>Globetrotters</u><br/><br/>\r\nA general quiz with travel flavour. The ultimate stop for any quizzing enthusiast who aspires to find frolic among other things in the midst of thrilling rounds. <br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<u>Remember the Titans</u> - Sports and Entertainment Quiz<br/><br/>\r\nThe SpEnt quiz held here at Ragam carves out a special place for itself in the midst of those who eat, drink, walk and talk sports. Challenging questions, thunderous applause and lightning speed response is what this is all about.<br/>\r\nBeing defensive serves no purpose.<br/> Attack those questions right from the front... <br/><br/>||sec||General Instructions||ttl||<ul>\r\n<li>Separate registration is available for participants who would like to participate only for quizzes.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The registration fee for each quiz is Rs. 50 per person.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Maximum of 3 participants per team for Open quizzes and 2 participants per team for College quizzes.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Those who have a valid Ragam 13 ID need not separately register for the quizzes.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>For the college quizzes valid college IDs should be shown at the time of participation. </li>\r\n</ul>||sec||Prize Money||ttl||First - INR 5000<br/>\r\nSecond - INR 3000<br/>\r\nThird - INR 1000<br/>\r\n(for all 4 quizzes)', 'quiz', 'Akhil Sanalkumar||@||9497426783||@||quiz||0||Sanjana Suresh Kumar||@||9497426792||@||quiz||0||||@||||@||quiz||0||', 'First - INR 5000<br/>\r\nSecond - INR 3000<br/>\r\nThi', '1||@||3', 0),
