('DBT', 'Debate', 6, 'Wise men argue cases, fools decide them. ', '<img src="/2013/images/events/Debate-Cartoon_resized.jpg" alt="Debate-Cartoon.jpg"/><br/>\r\n"Those who cannot understand how to put their thoughts on ice should not enter into the heat of debate."<br/>\r\n\r\n-Friedrich Nietzsche \r\n<br>\r\nBut even ice can&#39;t always quench the heat generated during debates at Ragam. Argue your points with tact and finesse and convince the audience and the judges to see things your way!\r\n<br/>\r\n||sec||Rules And Regulations||ttl||\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Separate event for the three languages (English/Hindi/Malayalam).</li>\r\n<li>One team per college.</li>\r\n<li>Two participants per team.</li>\r\n<li>One member speaks for the topic and the other against it.</li>\r\n<li>Topic will be given at least 4 hours prior to the event.</li>\r\n<li>5 minutes per speaker followed by questioning round.</li>\r\n<li>There will be rounds with exciting twists.</li>\r\n<li>Points: (15,10,6)</li>\r\n</ul>||sec||Prize Money||ttl||First - INR 4000  <br/>\r\nSecond - INR 2500 <br/>', 'debate, literary, talk, group discussion, fight', 'Nirmal Sabu||@||9895420189||@||debate||0||Pravar ||@||8086813352||@||debate||0||||@||||@||debate||0||', 'First - INR 4000  <br/>\r\nSecond - INR 2500 <br/>', '2||@||2', 0),
