('FIF', 'FIFA 13', 13, 'Challenging and addictive football game ', '<i>Football is an honest game.<br />\r\nItâ€™s true to life. Itâ€™s a game about sharing.<br /> \r\nFootball is a team game. So is life.<br />\r\nLetâ€™s see what you have, football lovers!<br /><br />\r\n</i>\r\n\r\nFIFA 13 (also known as FIFA Soccer 13 in North America) is the most recent edition of Electronic Arts&#39; highly-acclaimed association football FIFA video game series. Fast paced and with various skills and tricks to be mastered, this game has been a regular at gaming events since release. The soul and passion of the people&#39;s game is translated into FIFA. Though games are short - they are competitive and fun to watch, even by non-gamers. Score the most goals and kick your way to victory at this yearâ€™s Ragnarok!!!||sec||Rules and Regulations||ttl||<ul>\r\n<li>Registration fee is Rs. 80/- per participant. Ragam registration is compulsory. Registration will be closed after prelims.</li>\r\n<li>NFS and FIFA together can be registered for Rs 150/- per participant</li>\r\n<li>All games will be Classic 1 vs. 1 in multiplayer mode.</li>\r\n<li>There will be no practicing allowed. Participants are only allowed to change the necessary controls and check them.</li>\r\n<li>Only joystick controls are to be used, which will be provided.</li>\r\n<li>The total number of rounds will be decided by the participation.</li>\r\n<li>All rounds will follow usual knockout procedure.</li>\r\n<li>In case of a draw, the match is restarted with the golden goal rule (Same teams must be selected).</li>\r\n<li>In case of un-intentional disconnection, the admin will decide on how to proceed. In the game is within half-time and no goals have been scored, the game will be restarted with same teams for a full-time game. If not, the game will be played for the remaining time based on at what time it disconnected with scores being carried over.</li>\r\n<li>If at any time, a player intentionally disconnects/exits the game he/she will be disqualified. In case of alt-tabbing - the admin will decide whether it was intentional or a mistake and what action must be taken with disqualification being the maximum penalty.</li>\r\n<li>Teams can be either clubs or countries according to user&#39;s will.</li>\r\n<li>The first and second rounds will be classic 4 minute half time matches. The rest will all be 6 minute ones. Final match will be made a best of three.</li>\r\n<li>The administrator&#39;s decision will be final.</li>\r\n</ul>||sec||Prize Money||ttl||First - INR 3000<br/>\r\nSecond - INR 1500<br/>\r\nThird - INR 500<br/>', 'fifa, football, gaming  ', 'Vinayak R Kartha||@||7736539932||@||gaming||0||Jithin Thomas Paul||@||9496321073||@||gaming||0||||@||||@||gaming||0||', 'First - INR 3000<br/>\r\nSecond - INR 1500<br/>\r\nThi', '1||@||1', 0),
