('KPM', 'Kavithaparayanam', 6, 'Fascinate your listeners with the inner beauty of Malayalam poems.', '<img src="/2013/images/events/0_resized.jpg" alt="0.jpg"/><br/>\r\nDo you think you could accrue the beauty of vernacular on your lips?<br/>\r\nOr that you could capture the exemplary cadence of the ballad?<br/>\r\nThen here is the chance for you to enchant the most exquisite audience you can get.||sec||Rules and Regulations||ttl||\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Maximum 3 participants per college<br/></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Time limit : Maximum 10 minutes<br/></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Self written poems are also allowed, however extra points won&#39;t be awarded for the same<br/></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Judge&#39;s decision will be final<br/></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Points: (10, 6, 4)</li>\r\n</ul>||sec||Prize Money||ttl||First - INR 1500<br>\r\nSecond - INR 1000<br>\r\nThird - INR 750', 'kavithaparayanam, recitation, malayalam, poem, poets, ragam', 'Vijith N Nair ||@||9544981423||@||kavithaparayanam||0||Amala Maheshwari||@||9746920231||@||kavithaparayanam||0||||@||||@||kavithaparayanam||0||', 'First - INR 1500<br>\r\nSecond - INR 1000<br>\r\nThird', '1||@||1', 0),
('LMS', 'Light Music Solo', 9, 'You&#39;re on your own in singing this song!', '<img src="/2013/images/events/images(3)_resized.jpg" alt="images(3).jpg"/><br/>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n<i>Can you make the hearts go light,<br/>\r\n\r\nWith a music intense, sweet and bright?<br/>\r\n\r\nDon&#39;t you fear to stand up solo,<br/>\r\n\r\nFor your voice is what everyone will follow ! </i>\r\n\r\n\r\n||sec||Rules and Regulations||ttl||<ul>\r\n<li>One participant per college in each category (male and female)</li>\r\n<li>Time limit: 5 minutes per participant.</li>\r\n<li>The judging will be separate for male and female categories</li>\r\n<li>Film songs are not allowed.</li>\r\n<li>One (only) Instrumental accompaniment is permitted.</li>\r\n<li>Keyboard (piano patch only)/Electric Guitar may be provided if required.</li>\r\n<li>Points: (10, 6, 4)</li>\r\n</ul><br/>||sec||Prize Money||ttl||First - INR 2000<br>\r\nSecond - INR 1000<br>\r\n', 'light music, solo music, music, singing', 'Anjali S ||@||9497310480||@||lightmusicsolo||0||Vijith N||@||9544981423||@||lightmusicsolo||0||||@||||@||lightmusicsolo||0||', 'First - INR 2000<br>\r\nSecond - INR 1000<br>\r\n\r\n', '1||@||1', 0),
('LTG', 'Laser tag', 14, '', 'Ever thought it would be fun to shoot at people?<br/>\r\nTake it from us, it is. <br/><br/>\r\nTo this end, Ragam &#39;13 presents - the LazerTag Arena, a pitch dark canvas for you to bring Counter Strike action to real life. Here is the perfect spoil for all those battle tactics that succeeded in the virtual world to get the ultimate test - the real world. Form your teams and shoot the living daylights out of any unlucky soul that gets in your way.<br/><br/>\r\nLet those harrowing thoughts flow out of your brain and go for the kill here at Ragam &#39;13.<br/>\r\n', 'Laser, tag', 'Ajay||@||9497313813||@||lasertag||0||Rajiv Menon||@||9995799650||@||lasertag||0||||@||||@||lasertag||0||', '', '1||@||1', 0),
('MAC', 'Acoustics', 9, 'Play your favorite tune to mesmerize the crowd.', '<img src="/2013/images/events/Band(2)_resized.png" alt="Band(2).png"/>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n<i>Itâ€™s music in its purest and most divine form. <br/>\r\nFor men may come and men may go but those rhythms and beats live on forever.</i>||sec||Rules and Regulations||ttl||<ul>\r\n<li>Maximum of 12 participants per team.</li>\r\n<li>Time limit: 15 minutes + 3 minutes set-up time. </li>\r\n<li>Participating teams  should upload a video of any of their performance on YouTube and send its URL to acoustics@ragam.org.in  on or before March 7th, along with the following details:<br/>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>College/Band Name</li>\r\n<li>Name and Contact Info of the Team Leader</li>\r\n<li>List of Team members</li>\r\n</ul></li>  \r\n<li>Finalists will be screened based on the video sent. Registration will be confirmed only after receiving the confirmation letter.</li>\r\n<li>There is no On the Spot Registration.</li>\r\n<li>Teams are permitted to perform in the language of their choice. </li>\r\n<li>No electric instruments permitted apart from bass and electric guitar (clean). </li>\r\n<li>Keyboards are permitted only on piano patch.</li>\r\n<li>Points: (40, 30, 20)</li>\r\n\r\n</ul>||sec||Prize Money||ttl||First - INR 10000<br>\r\nSecond - INR 6000<br>\r\nThird - INR 4000', 'music, classical, redone, indian, acoustics ', 'Nirmal Sabu ||@||9895420189||@||acoustics||0||Aravind Nair||@||8891725632||@||acoustics||0||||@||||@||acoustics||0||', 'First - INR 10000<br>\r\nSecond - INR 6000<br>\r\nThir', '-||@||12', 0),
('MAP', 'Mappila Paattu', 9, 'a folklore muslim song competition', 'Capture the spirit of malabar with the most soulful renderings. Express the varied emotions of life through the &#39;ishals&#39; and &#39;prasams&#39;.<br/>||sec||Rules and Regulations||ttl||<ul>\r\n<li>Duration (Max): 5 minutes.</li>\r\n<li>Individual event.</li>\r\n<li>General types of permitted songs are Kess Pattu, Kissa Pattu and Kathu Pattu. </li>\r\n<li>The decision of the judges will be final and binding.</li>\r\n<li>Points: (10, 6, 4)</li>\r\n</ul>||sec||Prize Money||ttl||First - INR 1000<br/>\r\nSecond - INR 600<br/>\r\nThird - INR 400<br/>', 'mapila, paattu, mapila patu', 'Anjali S||@||9497310480||@||mappilapaattu||0||Akhil Sanalkumar||@||9497426783||@||mappilapaattu||0||||@||||@||mappilapaattu||0||', 'First - INR 1000<br/>\r\nSecond - INR 600<br/>\r\nThir', '1||@||1', 0),
('MEH', 'Mehendi', 10, 'Mehendi design competion', '<img src="/2013/images/events/Mehndi Designs for Hands_resized.jpg" alt="Mehndi Designs for Hands.jpg"/><br/>\r\n<br>\r\n<i>Create intricate patterns and gorgeous designs with this traditional adornment to bring out the beauty of an Indian woman&#39;s hands.</i><br/>\r\n<br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n||sec||Rules and Regulations||ttl||<ul>\r\n<li>Open event.</li>\r\n<li>On the spot registration allowed.</li>\r\n<li>Mehendi will be provided</li>\r\n<li>Participants may bring their own design</li>\r\n<li>Time limit: 60 minutes.</li>\r\n<li>Points: (10, 6, 4)</li>\r\n\r\n</ul>||sec||Prize Money||ttl||1st INR 1000 <br>  2nd  INR 600  <br> 3rd INR 400', 'mehendi , fine arts, art', 'Rohit Ka||@||9037685836||@||mehendi||0||Shuchi Sharda||@||9746918850||@||mehendi||0||||@||||@||mehendi||0||', '1st INR 1000 <br>  2nd  INR 600  <br> 3rd INR 400', '1||@||1', 0),
('MME', 'Mime', 8, 'Actions speak louder than words.', '<img src="/2013/images/events/Mime_resized.jpg" alt="Mime.jpg"/>\r\n<br/>\r\n<br/>\r\n<i>The world being divided by 6900 languages, this is the art which knows no barriers. The art which speaks its mind with everything but the tongue. Are you ready to be the actor who brings to stage, the plethora of expressions to state his thought?</i>||sec||Rules And Regulation||ttl||<ul>\r\n<li>One team per college</li>\r\n<li>Minimum 5 and maximum 9 members in a team (excluding those for background music)</li>\r\n<li>Time limit: 12 minutes empty to empty</li>\r\n<li>General rules of mime will be followed</li>\r\n<li>Instrumental accompanied is permitted</li>\r\n<li>Recordings are also allowed (to be submitted in mp3 or Audio format)</li>\r\n<li>Weightage will be given to themes and costumes</li>\r\n<li>Points (25, 15,10)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n||sec||Prize Money||ttl||First - INR 7000<br>\r\nSecond - INR 5000<br>\r\nThird - INR 3000', 'Mime, Drama, Acting, Dramatics', 'Rohit K A||@||871417225||@||mime||0||Sruthy Dileep ||@||9847068797||@||mime||0||||@||||@||mime||0||', 'First - INR 7000<br>\r\nSecond - INR 5000<br>\r\nThird', '5||@||9', 0);
