('MMR', 'Mimicry', 8, 'Strain your vocal chords.', '<i><img src="/2013/images/events/images (1) (1)_resized.jpg" alt="images (1) (1).jpg"/>\r\n<br/>\r\n<br/>\r\nWho steals the best from others, their signature style. <br/>\r\nThe lord of the thieves, shall win the trial.<br/>\r\n</i>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n||sec||RULES AND REGULATION||ttl||\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Two participants per college</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Vulgarity and obscenity shall be penalised</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Time limit : 6 minutes per participant</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Points: (10, 6, 4)</li>\r\n</ul>||sec||Prize Money||ttl||First - INR 1500<br>\r\nSecond - INR 1000<br>\r\nThird - INR 750', 'acting, drama, dramatics, monoact, act, mimicry, mimic ', 'Stebin Varghese||@||9995591911||@||mimicry||0||Lisha Fathima||@||9447538941||@||mimicry||0||||@||||@||mimicry||0||', 'First - INR 1500<br>\r\nSecond - INR 1000<br>\r\nThird', '1||@||1', 0),
('MOA', 'Monoact', 8, 'Embodiment of multiple characters', '<i><center><img src="/2013/images/events/monoact(1)_resized.jpg" alt="monoact(1).jpg"/></center><br><p>Acting is about letting another&#39;s emotions manifest your body language.<br></p>\r\n<p>Monoact is all about wielding your acting skills to transform yourself into multiple characters.</p></i>||sec||Rules and Regulations||ttl||<ul>\r\n<li>Two participants per college</li>\r\n <li>Vulgarity and obscenity shall be penalized</li>\r\n <li>Time limit: 6 minutes per participant</li>\r\n <li>Points: (10, 6, 4)</li>\r\n</ul>||sec||Prize Money||ttl||First - INR 1500<br>\r\nSecond - INR 1000<br> \r\nThird - INR 750', 'act, monoact, oneman show, monologue, single actor, imitate emotions', 'Gokul G Nair||@||8891699081||@||monoact||0||Amala Maheshwari||@||9746920231||@||monoact||0||||@||||@||monoact||0||', '1st - INR 1200<br>\r\n2nd - INR 800<br> \r\n3rd - INR ', '1||@||1', 0),
('MOS', 'Mafia On Stage', 11, 'Put yourself in the shoes of celebrities.', '<img src="/2013/images/events/mockpress_resized.jpg" alt="mockpress.jpg"/>\r\n<br>\r\n<i>Ever wondered how Osama-Bin Laden handled the media or what a personal interview with Dawood Ibrahim would be like. Stop wondering and start acting, for you are the most dreaded mafia leader. Live through the virtual environment of media and press with humor and wit, but beware,  the media is equally dangerous...</i>||sec||Rules and Regulations||ttl||<ul>\r\n\r\n<li>One team per college with 5 participants per team</li>\r\n<li>The characters:\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Joker from the Batman franchise</li>\r\n<li>Jack Sparrow</li>\r\n<li>P.V Narayanan aka Pavanai from Nadodikattu</li>\r\n<li>Don Vito Corleone aka The Godfather</li>\r\n<li>Gabbar Singh from Sholay</li>\r\n<li>Osama Bin Laden</li>\r\n<li>The Don (Shahrukh Khan)</li>\r\n<li>Sagar alias Jacky (Mohanlal)</li>\r\n<li>Big B (Mammootty)</li>\r\n<li>Lara Croft from Tomb Raider</li>\r\n<li>Bellatrix Lestrange from Harry Potter</li>\r\n<li>Mrs Smith from Mrn Mrs Smith</li>\r\n<li>Nagavalli from Manichitrathazhu</li>\r\n<li>Kamini (Kareena Kapoor) from Don</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li><li>Event held along with fancy dress</li>\r\n<li>Judging will be done in two rounds</li>\r\n<li>The first round will be a press conference with all the characters</li>\r\n<li>Round two will be a surprise round the rules of which will be given on the spot</li>\r\n<li>Judging criterion:</li>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Similarity to the character</li>\r\n<li>Humor and spontaneity</li>\r\n<li>Vulgarity will be penalized</li>\r\n<li>The decision of the judges will be final</li>\r\n<li>Points:(10,6,4)</li>\r\n</ol>||sec||Prize Money||ttl||First - INR 4000<br/>\r\nSecond - INR 2500<br/>\r\nThird - INR 1500<br/>', 'mock, press, celebrity', 'Nirmal Sabu||@||9895420189||@||mafiaonstage||0||Akhil Sanalkumar||@||9497426783||@||mafiaonstage||0||Yashwanth||@||8086817884||@||mafiaonstage||0||', '', '4||@||6', 0),
('MRG', 'Mr and Ms Ragam', 5, 'To test your mettle and prove your worth!', '<img src="/2013/images/events/mr_and_mrs_smith__ft_style_by_misstirius-d572jc6_resized.png" alt="mr_and_mrs_smith__ft_style_by_misstirius-d572jc6.png"/>\r\n<br>\r\nDo you have what it takes to stand out in a crowd?<br/>\r\nImpress us with your vibrant personality and claim the ultimate title of Ragam. ||sec||Rules and Regulations||ttl||<ul>\r\n<li>No limit in the number of participants per college.</li>\r\n<li>3 boys & 3 girls get on stage for the final showdown.</li>\r\n<li>The fine line between humour and vulgarity shall be respected.</li>\r\n<li>Judges&#39; decision is final & binding.</li>\r\n<li>Points: (30) for each</li>\r\n</ul>||sec||Prize Money||ttl||INR 3000 for each', 'personality, ragam, spotlight', 'Akhil Sanalkumar||@||9497426783||@||mrandmsragam||0||Yadu Aravind Menon||@||9746398389||@||mrandmsragam||0||Nitheesh I S||@||9497269030||@||mrandmsragam||0||', ' INR 3000 for each', '1||@||1', 0),
('MSP', 'Movie Spoof', 8, 'create hilarious spoofs of movies', 'Mix and match your favorite movies and create spoofs that are way more hilarious than the original versions.||sec||Rules and Regulations||ttl||<ul>\r\n<li>One team per college</li>\r\n<li>Maximum of 8 members in a team</li>\r\n<li>Props are allowed</li>\r\n<li>English/Hindi/Malayalam may be used as a medium of narration</li>\r\n<li>Back stage narration (live/recorded) is allowed </li>\r\n<li>Background music is permitted</li>\r\n<li>No microphones on stage</li>\r\n<li>Time limit: 8 minutes empty to empty</li>\r\n<li>Points: (20, 15, 10)</li>\r\n</ul> ||sec||Prize Money||ttl||First - INR 2000<br/>\r\nSecond - INR 1500 <br/>', 'movie, spoof, film spoof', 'Jain Abraham||@||9496217808||@||moviespoof||0||John Joseph||@||8129038009||@||moviespoof||0||||@||||@||moviespoof||0||', 'First - INR 2000<br/>\r\nSecond - INR 1500 <br/>', '1||@||8', 0),
('MWS', 'Western Solo', 9, 'Sing a solo from the occident.', '\r\n<img src="/2013/images/events/woman-singing-microphone-vintage-525_resized.jpg" alt="woman-singing-microphone-vintage-525.jpg"/>\r\n<i><br>\r\nPour out the liquid music of your voice,<br/>\r\nEnrapture the crowd with your little dew-drops of melody,<br/>\r\n\r\nPursue your dream and charm your way to stardom,<br/>\r\n\r\nAnd be the talent the world has never seen!<br/></i>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n||sec||Rules and Regulations||ttl||<ul>\r\n<li>One participant per college in each category(male &female)<br/></li>\r\n\r\n<li>The judging will be separate for male and female categories</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Time limit: 5 minutes per participant.<br/></li>\r\n<li>One (only) Instrumental accompaniment is permitted.</li>\r\n<li>Keyboard (piano patch only)/Electric Guitar may be provided if required.<br/></li>\r\n<li>Points: (10, 6, 4)</li>\r\n</ul>||sec||Prize Money||ttl||First - INR 2000<br>\r\nSecond - INR 1000<br>\r\n\r\n', 'western solo, song, music', 'Surya Rajan||@||9633721575||@||westernsolo||0||Maria Mathew||@||8891218010||@||westernsolo||0||||@||||@||westernsolo||0||', 'First - INR 2000<br>\r\nSecond - INR 1000<br>\r\n', '1||@||1', 0),
('NFS', 'NFS: Most Wanted', 13, 'Outdrive your friends and outsmart your rivals!', '<i>The winner ain&#39;t the one with the fastest car;<br /> \r\nItâ€™s the one who refuses to lose. <br />\r\nWill it be the same with you? <br />\r\nShow your guts and adrenaline at Ragnarok!! <br /><br />\r\n</i>\r\nNeed for Speed: Most Wanted (commonly known as NFS: MW) is a racing video game featuring street racing-oriented game play. Easily among the most popular racing games of all times, this instant classic has had players enchanted ever since its release. <br/>\r\nThough many iterations has come out in the NFS series, NFS: MW remains an all-time favourite because of its competitive nature and gamers have been known to keep practicing to shave off those crucial milliseconds off their lap times. Being a racing game, it&#39;s easy to pick up and play and the adrenaline rush of speeding along and sweeping into the pole position is known to all. \r\n||sec||Rules and Regulations||ttl||<ul>\r\n<li>Registration fee is Rs. 80/- per participant. Ragam registration is compulsory. Registration will be closed after prelims.</li>\r\n<li>NFS and FIFA together can be registered for Rs 150/- per participant</li><br/>\r\n<u>Qualification Round:</u><br/><br/>\r\n<li>All Tournament participants will play 3 laps and the qualifier for further rounds will be decided by the best time basis! (TOP 16).</li>\r\n<li>Players can choose their cars, customize them and modify them.</li>\r\n<li>Race course: Dunwich Bay.</li>\r\n<li>At the end of each match, players must maintain the final screens and receive confirmation from a referee.</li>\r\n<li>Any participant failing to complete the race will be disqualified.</li><br/>\r\n<u>Common Rules for Competitive rounds, Semi-finals and Finals:</u><br/><br/>\r\n<li>Game Type: Circuit</li>\r\n<li>No. of Laps: 3</li>\r\n<li>Courses: Courses will be given at random and will be given on the spot. ( Players will be informed before the tournament of any such modifications)</li>\r\n<li>Participants are not allowed to use their own profiles, only Immolation provided save files can be used for car setting.</li>\r\n<li>Players will be given 2 minutes to setup the car and its performance before the game.</li><br/>\r\n<u>Competitive Rounds:</u><br/><br/>\r\n<li>There will be two levels: level 1 (all 16 qualifiers), and level 2 (top 8 from level 1).</li>\r\n<li>Courses: Heritage Heights, Diamond, Switchback, East Park, Omega, Dunwich Bay, Oil Refinery, Bay Bridge and Clubhouse.</li>\r\n<li>Competition: All qualifying participants will compete in a "Circuit" mode in groups of 4 on LAN.</li>\r\n<li>LEVEL 1: The first two players to finish all 3 laps will qualify to the next round (level 2).</li>\r\n<li>LEVEL 2: The player, who finishes first, will qualify for the semi-finals.</li><br/>\r\n<u>Semi-Finals:</u><br/><br/>\r\n<li>Courses: Heritage Heights, Diamond, East Park, Dunwich Bay, Bay Bridge and oil refinery.</li>\r\n<li>Competition: All 4 qualifying participants will compete together in 6 races in "Circuit" mode on LAN.</li>\r\n<li>Winning a race: The winner of a race is the first player to complete 3 laps of the circuit course and cross the finish line.</li>\r\n<li>Qualifying: The 2 players winning at-least 2 races will be qualified for the finals.</li><br/>\r\n<u>Finals:</u><br/><br/>\r\n<li>Courses: Heritage Heights, Diamond, East Park, Dunwich Bay and Bay Bridge.</li>\r\n<li>Competition: All qualifying participants will compete 1 vs. 1 in 5 races in "Circuit" mode on LAN.</li>\r\n<li>Winning a race: The winner of a race is the first player to complete 3 laps of the circuit course and cross the finish line.</li>\r\n<li>Winning the tournament: A player winning 3 races out of 5 will be the "winner" of the tournament.</li><br/>\r\n<u>Other specifications:</u><br/><br/>\r\n<li>Race Mode Options:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Track Direction : Forward/Backward</li>\r\n<li>LAPS : 3</li>\r\n<li>N20 : On</li>\r\n<li>Collision Detection : Off</li>\r\n<li>Performance Matching : On</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Use of any cheat program is not allowed. Use of Carrera GT and BMW GTR is not allowed. Use of Junkman upgrades is not allowed. Use of any settings exceeding standard and permitted settings is not allowed.</li>\r\n<li>If the match is disrupted due to unnecessary chatting, the player may be given a warning or lose by default at the referee&#39;s sole discretion. Two warnings constitute being disqualified from the tournament.</li>\r\n<li>Any disconnection of the connection between matches players due to System, Network, PC, and/or Power problems/issues results into a restart of match. If any player does not agree to a match restart, that player will lose by default.</li>\r\n<li>Intentional disconnection will not be tolerated. Upon judgment by the referee, any offending player will be charged with a loss by forfeit.</li>\r\n</ul>||sec||Prize Money||ttl||First - INR 3000<br/>\r\nSecond - INR 1500<br/>\r\nThird - INR 500<br/>', 'NFS, Car race, Most Wanted, NFSMW, gaming', 'Vinayak R Kartha||@||7736539932||@||gaming||0||Sairam Arunachalam||@||8891725696||@||gaming||0||||@||||@||gaming||0||', 'First - INR 3000<br/>\r\nSecond - INR 1500<br/>\r\nThi', '1||@||1', 0),
('OPN', 'Oppana', 7, 'a mappila dance competition', 'This event lets you recreate all the colours and charms of Oppana, the traditional Muslim art form of Kerala.<br/>\r\nMesmerize the crowd by the boundless grace of the bride and the glorious moves around her.<br/>||sec||Rules and Regulations||ttl||<ul>\r\n<li>Duration (Max) : 15 minutes</li>\r\n<li>Participant shall bring all required costumes. </li>\r\n<li>Participant shall hand over the recorded song for the Dance on a pen drive or a CD to the Event Coordinator at least 30 minutes in advance. </li>\r\n<li>Group of minimum 5 and maximum 12 members.</li>\r\n<li>The team shall consist of 1 manavatti, 1 main singer, 2 chorus singers and a maximum of 8 dancers for girls teams.</li>\r\n<li>The team shall consist of 1 manavaalan and a maximum of 10 dancers of which one should be the main singer, for boys teams. </li>\r\n<li>Members of the team need not necessarily be from the same college (but in this case, the colleges in consideration wonâ€™t receive any points).</li>\r\n<li>No stage setting permitted. </li>\r\n<li>Songs should not be album songs.</li>\r\n<li>Points: (25, 15, 10)</li>\r\n</ul>||sec||Prize Money||ttl||First - INR 3500<br/>\r\nSecond - INR 2000<br/>', 'oppanai, opana,', 'Vijith N Nair||@||9544981423||@||oppana||0||Akhil Sanalkumar||@||9497426783||@||oppana||0||||@||||@||oppana||0||', 'First - INR 3500<br/>\r\nSecond - INR 2000<br/>', '5||@||12', 0),
